name: Cutter Shark
desc: You can target 1 WATER monster you control; Special Summon 1 Fish monster with the same Level, but with a different name, from your Deck, but it cannot activate its effects this turn, also you cannot Special Summon monsters from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn, except Xyz Monsters. You can only use this effect of "Cutter Shark" once per turn. This card can be treated as a Level 3 or 5 monster when used for the Xyz Summon of a WATER monster.
